<h1>
	Welcome to Strepco of Cleveland</h1>
<img src="/content/1.jpg" class="img_float" />
<img src="/content/3.jpg" class="img_float" />
<p>
	Welcome to America's premier <span class="inline_h">strapping tool repair</span> facility. We take the run-around out of strapping tool repairs. We are one of the few companies in the United States repairing "All Lines" of strapping tools. Some of the <span class="inline_h">popular brands we repair</span> are:</p>
<ul>
	<li>Acme</li>
	<li>Acme/Rapz</li>
	<li>Rapz </li>
	<li>Delta </li>
	<li>Signode</li>
	<li>Gerrard</li>
	<li>Fromm </li>
	<li>Orgapack</li>
	<li>Titan </li>
	<li>Samuel</li>
	<li>Polychem</li>
	</ul>
<p>
	<span class="inline_h">Do not throw away tools that might seem to you to be too old, or obsolete!</span> We might have the solution to repair those <span class="inline_h">strapping tools and packaging tools.</span></p>
<p>
	We have been in business since 1979, and recently move our business to a new facility, effective July 1, 2006.</p>
<p>
	Also we are a distributor for <span class="inline_h">new, rebuilt and refurbished strapping tools</span>. Some of the <span class="inline_h">new tool lines</span> we carry in stock are:</p>
<ul>
	<li>Acme</li>
	<li>Delta</li>
	<li>Orgapack</li>
	<li>Fromm</li>
	<li>MIP (Midwest Industrial Packaging)</li>
	</ul>
<p>
	If you need accessories such as <span class="inline_h">strapping dispensers, strap cutters, or tool balancers</span>, in order to suspend combination tools, we have those too!</p>
<p>
	Whether you prefer to e-mail, phone, or fax us, our customer service representatives, and technicians are standing by to help you.</p>

